<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 12:11:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>新传记称，英国女王伊丽莎白二世为儿子查尔斯留下了密封的临终信</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/queen-elizabeth-ii-left-sealed-death-bed-letter-for-son-charles-claims-new-biography/articleshow/106814213.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106814213.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据报道，女王伊丽莎白二世于 2022 年 9 月去世，她为她的儿子兼继承人国王查理三世留下了一封密封的临终遗言。传记作家罗伯特·哈德曼在他关于女王去世后立即发生的后果的新书中揭示了这一点。女王一直在处理她的官方信件直到最后，她最后的红盒子里装着一封给新国王的私人信件。这封信的内容尚不清楚，但据信包含最后的指示或告别。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 11:42:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/queen-elizabeth-ii-left-sealed-death-bed-letter-for-son-charles-claims-new-biography/articleshow/106814213.cms</guid></item><item><title>数着日子：哈马斯人质的家人准备庆祝亲人被囚禁一百天</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/counting-the-days-families-of-hamas-hostages-prepare-to-mark-loved-ones-100th-day-in-captivity/articleshow/106813111.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106813111.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;雷切尔·戈德堡-波林继续不懈地努力将她的儿子和其他被哈马斯武装分子扣押的人质带回家。她的儿子赫什·戈德堡-波林在一次以色列音乐节上被从加沙冲过边境的武装分子绑架。虽然一些人质在停火期间被释放，但仍有 132 名人质仍被关押。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 10:58:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/counting-the-days-families-of-hamas-hostages-prepare-to-mark-loved-ones-100th-day-in-captivity/articleshow/106813111.cms</guid></item><item><title>俾路支亚克贾赫蒂委员会发起运动以获得全球支持</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/baloch-yakjahti-committee-launches-campaign-to-garner-global-support-against-enforced-disappearances/articleshow/106811861.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106811861.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俾路支 Yakjehti 委员会 (BYC) 发起了一项名为 #IStandWithBalochMarch 的社交媒体活动，以提高人们对其反对俾路支省强迫失踪的运动的认识并获得支持。该活动旨在消除虚假信息，消除具有破坏性的谣言，并强调该地区的法外处决和强迫失踪问题。来自马里尔和利亚里的俾路支妇女和儿童表现出了团结，政治活动家 Mahrang Baloch 计划向联合国特别报告员报告这一虐待事件。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 10:14:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/baloch-yakjahti-committee-launches-campaign-to-garner-global-support-against-enforced-disappearances/articleshow/106811861.cms</guid></item><item><title>他们不是外星人。这是秘鲁官员的判决，他们没收了两个玩偶</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/theyre-not-aliens-thats-the-verdict-from-peru-officials-who-seized-2-doll-like-figures/articleshow/106811815.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106811815.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 10:12:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/theyre-not-aliens-thats-the-verdict-from-peru-officials-who-seized-2-doll-like-figures/articleshow/106811815.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国努力影响以色列对待巴勒斯坦人的态度。为什么本杰明·内塔尼亚胡不太可能屈服</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/the-us-struggles-to-sway-israel-on-its-treatment-of-palestinians-why-benjamin-netanyahu-is-unlikely-to-yield/articleshow/106803217.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106803217.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乔·拜登总统的政府不断敦促以色列在加沙战斗结束后重新与巴勒斯坦人建立伙伴关系，并支持他们最终独立。本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理一直说不。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:34:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/the-us-struggles-to-sway-israel-on-its-treatment-of-palestinians-why-benjamin-netanyahu-is-unlikely-to-yield/articleshow/106803217.cms</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰一夜之间遭到 40 枚俄罗斯导弹和无人机袭击 - 空军</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-attacked-overnight-by-40-russian-missiles-drones-air-force/articleshow/106811424.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106811424.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;乌克兰-危机-乌克兰一夜之间遭到40枚俄罗斯导弹和无人机的袭击-空军</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:57:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/ukraine-attacked-overnight-by-40-russian-missiles-drones-air-force/articleshow/106811424.cms</guid></item><item><title>尼日利亚丹格特炼油厂在拖延多年后开始生产</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigerias-dangote-refinery-starts-production-after-years-of-delays/articleshow/106811346.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106811346.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:53:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/nigerias-dangote-refinery-starts-production-after-years-of-delays/articleshow/106811346.cms</guid></item><item><title>南非非国大在艰难的选举年之前庆祝成立 112 周年</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-africas-ruling-party-marks-its-112th-anniversary-ahead-of-a-tough-election-year/articleshow/106811143.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106811143.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;南非执政党非洲人国民大会在即将举行的全国选举之前庆祝其成立 112 周年。正在寻求连任的总统西里尔·拉马福萨将概述该党今年的纲领。非国大因未能向该国大多数贫困人口提供基本服务以及腐败指控而面临批评。民意调查显示，该党可能很难在执政期间首次获得超过 50% 的选票。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:46:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-africas-ruling-party-marks-its-112th-anniversary-ahead-of-a-tough-election-year/articleshow/106811143.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国：布法罗超市大规模枪击案造成至少10人死亡 枪手面临死刑</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-gunman-in-buffalo-supermarket-mass-shooting-who-killed-at-least-10-to-face-death-penalty/articleshow/106810622.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106810622.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据半岛电视台报道，一名 20 岁男子在纽约州杀害了 10 名黑人，并现场直播了超市暴乱，他将面临美国联邦检察官的死刑。检察官透露，袭击者在进入杂货店之前，在停车场开枪射击了四人，其中三人伤重不治。死者中有八名顾客、商店保安人员和一名协助顾客搬运物资的教堂执事。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-gunman-in-buffalo-supermarket-mass-shooting-who-killed-at-least-10-to-face-death-penalty/articleshow/106810622.cms</guid></item><item><title>皮尤研究中心：亚裔美国人是美国增长最快的合格选民群体</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/asian-americans-fastest-growing-group-of-eligible-voters-in-us-pew-research/articleshow/106810950.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106810950.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;过去二十年里，符合资格的亚裔选民人数大幅增加，最近的调查结果显示自 2020 年以来这一数字持续增加。根据皮尤研究中心题为“2024 年亚裔美国人合格选民的关键事实”的研究报告，亚裔美国人选民人数过去四年里，合格选民群体扩大了 15%。该研究强调，相当一部分亚裔美国人由于非美国公民身份而没有投票资格，这使得他们与普通民众相比参与选举过程的可能性较小。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/asian-americans-fastest-growing-group-of-eligible-voters-in-us-pew-research/articleshow/106810950.cms</guid></item><item><title>土耳其对伊拉克和叙利亚的库尔德武装发动空袭，造成9名士兵死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-launches-airstrikes-against-kurdish-militants-in-iraq-and-syria-after-9-soldiers-killed/articleshow/106810436.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106810436.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;土耳其军事基地遭到袭击后，土耳其国防部对伊拉克和叙利亚的库尔德武装分子进行了空袭。此次空袭旨在消除针对土耳其的恐怖袭击，确保边境安全。土耳其政府一直在对库尔德工人党（PKK）发动罢工，该党是一个被取缔的库尔德分裂主义组织。据土耳其官员报道，与库尔德工人党有联系的武装分子试图侵入伊拉克北部的土耳其基地。该事件导致六名士兵死亡。额外的冲突夺去了另外六名土耳其士兵的生命。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:16:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/turkey-launches-airstrikes-against-kurdish-militants-in-iraq-and-syria-after-9-soldiers-killed/articleshow/106810436.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国煤矿事故已造成8人死亡、8人失踪 救援工作正在进行中</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/8-people-killed-8-more-missing-in-china-coal-mine-accident-rescue-ops-underway/articleshow/106807958.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106807958.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据新华社周五援引地方当局的消息称，中国河南省平顶山市一煤矿发生事故，造成至少八人死亡、八人失踪。周五下午2时55分，事件发生时，平顶山天安煤业有限公司煤矿内共有425人。新华社报道称，380名被困矿工已被安全救出，初步调查显示，事故系煤与瓦斯突出所致。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:39:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/8-people-killed-8-more-missing-in-china-coal-mine-accident-rescue-ops-underway/articleshow/106807958.cms</guid></item><item><title>经过多年的拖延，新西兰前总理杰辛达·阿德恩喜结良缘</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/former-new-zealand-pm-jacinda-ardern-ties-the-knot-in-private-ceremony-clarke-gayford/articleshow/106807392.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106807392.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;新西兰前总理杰辛达·阿德恩 (Jacinda Ardern) 与她的长期伴侣克拉克·盖福德 (Clarke Gayford) 在周六的私人仪式上喜结良缘。婚礼因 Covid-19 大流行而推迟，在风景如画的霍克斯湾地区的一个豪华葡萄园举行，远离首都惠灵顿。这对夫妇对活动的细节保密，只有亲密的家人、朋友和阿德恩的一些前同事出席。客人中有阿德恩的继任者、前总理克里斯·希普金斯(Chris Hipkins)。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:26:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/former-new-zealand-pm-jacinda-ardern-ties-the-knot-in-private-ceremony-clarke-gayford/articleshow/106807392.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾总统蔡英文投票，敦促选民投票并为国家做出决定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-president-tsai-ing-wen-casts-vote-urges-voters-to-turn-out-and-decide-for-nation/articleshow/106806715.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106806715.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据亚洲新闻台报道，台湾总统蔡英文周六早上在新北市投票，敦促人们投票。民进党领袖在新北秀朗国小投票点投票。副总统候选人萧美琴和几名党内官员也在场。蔡英文向早期选民致意，称赞天气好，并鼓励大家投票。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 06:58:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-president-tsai-ing-wen-casts-vote-urges-voters-to-turn-out-and-decide-for-nation/articleshow/106806715.cms</guid></item><item><title>也门胡塞武装的神秘领导人阿卜杜勒·马利克·胡塞是谁？</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-is-abdul-malik-al-houthi-the-enigmatic-leader-of-yemens-houthi-fighters/articleshow/106804850.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106804850.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;也门胡塞武装领导人阿卜杜勒·马利克·胡塞自 2015 年以来一直与沙特领导的联军作战。他将农村叛乱民兵转变为一支有弹性的武装团体，获得了战斗机、武装无人机和导弹。胡塞运动为统治也门一千年的扎伊迪什叶派而战。他们在马里布发动了大规模攻势。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 06:17:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/who-is-abdul-malik-al-houthi-the-enigmatic-leader-of-yemens-houthi-fighters/articleshow/106804850.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾走钢丝已成刀刃</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-tightrope-has-become-a-knife-edge/articleshow/106802741.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106802741.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾即将举行的选举以及中美关系的恶化正在威胁台湾的韧性、创新和团结。台湾陷入了来自中国的生存威胁和对美国保卫台湾的承诺的怀疑之间。关键技术的竞争以及禁止向中国大陆销售高科技产品也对台湾半导体行业产生了影响。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:21:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwans-tightrope-has-become-a-knife-edge/articleshow/106802741.cms</guid></item><item><title>拜登政府要求SC告诉德克萨斯州停止阻止美国边境人员巡逻</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-administration-asks-supreme-court-to-tell-texas-to-stop-blocking-us-border-agents-from-patrols/articleshow/106801114.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106801114.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;司法部周五要求最高法院命令德克萨斯州停止阻止边境巡逻人员进入近几个月来大量移民越过的美墨边境部分地区，这引发了共和党州长格雷格·阿博特和德克萨斯州之间的另一场摊牌。拜登政府的移民执法问题。该请求是在德克萨斯州竖起围栏以控制伊格尔帕斯里奥格兰德河沿岸近 50 英亩（20 公顷）的公园之后提出的。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 04:36:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/biden-administration-asks-supreme-court-to-tell-texas-to-stop-blocking-us-border-agents-from-patrols/articleshow/106801114.cms</guid></item><item><title>台湾选民在民意调查中选择下一个总统，权衡中国的威胁和岛屿的稳定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-voters-choosing-next-president-in-poll-weighing-chinas-threat-and-islands-stability/articleshow/106799019.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106799019.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;台湾人周六将在选举中投票选出新总统和立法机构，这次选举可能会描绘出这个自治民主国家未来四年与中国关系的轨迹。该岛距离中国海岸 160 公里（100 英里），北京声称拥有该岛的主权，必要时将用武力夺回该岛，该岛的和平与稳定受到威胁。经济低迷和房价昂贵等国内问题也在竞选中占据了显着位置。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 03:31:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/taiwan-voters-choosing-next-president-in-poll-weighing-chinas-threat-and-islands-stability/articleshow/106799019.cms</guid></item><item><title>新成立的巴基斯坦独立党宣布旁遮普邦议会席位候选人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/newly-formed-istehkam-e-pakistan-party-announces-candidates-for-national-punjab-assembly-seats/articleshow/106802447.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106802447.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;最近成立的巴基斯坦独立党（IPP）在与巴基斯坦穆斯林联盟纳瓦兹（PML-N）进行席位调整后，宣布了全国和旁遮普议会席位的候选人。由贾汉吉尔·塔林 (Jahangir Tareen) 领导的该党已派出 12 名候选人角逐国民议会席位，27 名候选人角逐旁遮普省议会席位。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/newly-formed-istehkam-e-pakistan-party-announces-candidates-for-national-punjab-assembly-seats/articleshow/106802447.cms</guid></item><item><title>布林肯敦促中国在台湾投票时保持两岸稳定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-urges-china-to-maintain-cross-strait-stability-as-taiwan-votes/articleshow/106795644.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/106795644.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯周五在与中国高级官员会面时要求北京保持两岸稳定，此时距离台湾选民投票选出新总统只有几个小时。布林肯在最近的中东危机之行和参加达沃斯世界经济论坛之间短暂返回华盛顿，会见了中国共产党中央委员会国际部主任刘建超。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 02:06:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/blinken-urges-china-to-maintain-cross-strait-stability-as-taiwan-votes/articleshow/106795644.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>